attributes.title: BEWAREEE OF TRUMP
attributes.review: I downloaded the app a week ago. It has been the craziest week of my life. I was sitting on the toilet when I decided to download this app. 3 hours later I decided to go on a walk with my pet caterpillar. After that I ate a sandwich. Then I decided to watch some movies! THEN OUT OF NOWHERE Tᖇᑌᗰᑭ broke through my window I screamed! But he cut off my toes. Then he started singing Gabbie Hannah. I was scared he kidnapped me and brought me back to the White House. He made me clean up his bread crumbs and pick up his old gym socks. I cried everyday for about a week.Then out of nowhere Barron trump came to save me!!! He showed me an escape route! I begged him to come with me and escape his evil orange father! He refused. To this day I still have memories of  Donald singing gabbies song and having to pick up his crumbs. 😿✨💔
